| The documents that are currently WIP should be improved to have a complete introduction.I was lucky to also implement Rocket modules for the first time while I participated in this training. These pages have been useful to locate the modules that I had to look for. A hands-on learning opportunity would elevate the training process for newcomers, there are too many modules discussed here so it is not easy to comprehend the Rocket flow in detail.Having FAQ sections under module documentations are a great idea, but they are mostly relevant to usage of parameters for certain purposes. From a delivery DS point of view, I learned how to implement extensions via my teammates with prior Rocket implementation experience and #ask channels. This training could include pages that would guide the trainees on how to add some custom data to internal-data, then connect it to the relevant modules of Rocket, and to add the extension via pipeline overrides

, then connect it to the relevant modules of Rocket, and to add the extension via pipeline overrides. People with more experience on implementation with Rocket may also have suggestions to include additional key points that fill any gaps in the training. |
